title: The Art of Driftwood and Dried Arrangements (Art Ebook).pdf
description:
Crown | 1951 | Pdf | Eng | 143 pages | 20.4 MB

This book has been three years in the making. In that time I have collected a studio full of driftwood pieces. Many of them, by now, are old friendshandled and used in countless ways, countless times. Photographs have piled up by the hundreds. The editing and final selection have not been easy, but many friendly critics have helped in making the choices published here
